<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ka harnak vialte Jesuh ka chimh lai, Ka thilrit kei lawng ka phor kho
 lo, Ka lung retheih lioah a ka bawmh lai, A ka dawt i a ka ruah zungzal.

[C1]
   Jesuh ka chimh lai, Jesuh ka chimh lai, Ka thilrit kei lawng ka phor
   kho lo. Jesuh ka chimh lai! Jesuh ka chimh lai Jesuh lawng bawm kho tu cu
   a si.

[V2]
 Ka temh innak cu Jesuh ka chimh lai, Amah cu zawn ruah nak he a khat,
 Bawmhnak ka hal ah cun a ka khamh lai, Ka temh innak cu a donghter lai.

[C2]
   Jesuh ka chimh lai, Jesuh ka chimh lai, Ka thilrit kei lawng ka phor
   kho lo. Jesuh ka chimh lai! Jesuh ka chimh lai Jesuh lawng bawm kho tu cu
   a si.

[V3]
 Hneksaknak chungin Khamhu Bawi ka herh, Ka thilrit vialte chawng kho
 tu cu, Jesuh ka chimh lai, Jesuh ka chimh lai, Ngaihchiatnak vialte a ka
 chan lai.

[C3]
   Jesuh ka chimh lai, Jesuh ka chimh lai, Ka thilrit kei lawng ka phor
   kho lo. Jesuh ka chimh lai! Jesuh ka chimh lai Jesuh lawng bawm kho tu cu
   a si.

[V4]
 Vawlei nuamhnak nih an ka lem lengmang, Sualnak tuah dingin an ka lem
 tawn Jesuh ka chimh lai i, a ka hruai lai, Vawlei vialte ka tei khawh
 nakhnga.

[C4]
   Jesuh ka chimh lai, Jesuh ka chimh lai, Ka thilrit kei lawng ka phor
   kho lo. Jesuh ka chimh lai! Jesuh ka chimh lai Jesuh lawng bawm kho tu cu
   a si.</lyrics>
<key>Eb</key>
<title>JESUH KA CHIMH LAI CH398</title>
<hymn_number>398</hymn_number>
</song>